oads/2024/04/Moshpit@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Moshpit@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>美国的一个摇滚音乐节宣布，2024 年的音乐节将首次增加指定的狂欢区。</p><p>在威斯康星州卡多特举行的摇滚节历来一直坚持对 Mosh 进行限制——在其分期中禁止 Moshpit、死亡墙、死亡圈等。</p><p>然而，今年的赛事已确定将放宽限制，并引入允许人群活动的指定区域。</p><p>直到今年，摇滚节的政策还规定该活动是“非狂欢节”，任何形式的狂欢都会“导致腕带被摘除并被移出音乐节场地”。它解释说，这是因为将节日观众的安全作为“优先事项”。</p><p>然而，周一（巧合的是愚人节），音乐节告诉投注者，今年的规则已经放宽，并且将引入狂欢区，但仅限于百威 Boneyard 舞台。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C5PPoagBhay/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,3